{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't think-- I don't think they were hung, I think they were mostly shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't remember anybody being hung.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But basically, it was a very Spartan existence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We lived in a big barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't know quite what to do with us, because we were kids, a lot of kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They use-- they used to sort of chase us all over the place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know, from one end to the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know quite what the purpose behind it was, because they couldn't really send us out to-- to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, we were too young for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I think they wanted to get it over as soon as possible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I think-- I don't think they knew themselves how-- why we were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And after about six weeks in this camp, we were all called to be put on the train to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were together, actually, we were called together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My cousin, myself, my sister, my uncle, and my aunt, and-- and-- not my-- not my older cousin, Ruth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She-- she was working in the Phillips works, so she remained in Vught.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But the rest of us, Alfred, myself, and my Uncle Max, and my Aunt Paula were sent to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1943.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say it was in early spring, probably.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we got to Westerbork, it was on a Monday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why do I know it was a Monday?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the next day-- every Tuesday, there were trains to-- they're the transport to east to Auschwitz, or to Sobibor, which I found out later.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we arrived on a Monday evening, and my cousin and myself were separated from the rest of the family, put up in a different barracks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if-- if my sister was with my aunt or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know, but I-- she wasn't with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And during the night from this particular barracks, they were called-- people were called to go on the transport the next day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And our name was called also, myself and-- and Alfred's name, very clearly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I know, Fred Spiegel called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was my name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Alfred Spiegel.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And most of the people in the barracks were called, and most of them-- that's what they often did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- you came from one place, and they right of way tried to get rid of you to the-- to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because in Westerbork, people always tried to get to deferment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And once you established yourself, you managed often to get a longer deferment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, we were called, and I know that my uncle had always been afraid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had heard of transfers east to Poland, and he had been on the Russian front in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he knew what it-- what it was all about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very much afraid, you know, because he knew that Poland was-- aside from the Germans being there, it was known for its anti-Semitism so he knew it wasn't a good place to go to.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I know they told you work camps and all that, but--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were called in early dawn, and we were walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were sort of isolated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "During the days-- in the day when the transport left, you were not allowed to speak.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed to speak to you, you're not allowed to speak to anybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed to go out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were confined to the barracks with people who didn't go on the transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You walked along certain paths guarded by Dutch police and German SS with dogs, and also with Jewish police, camp police, OK?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were walking along there, and I was very scared because, well, first of what my uncle had said.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Number two, everybody else was scared so it didn't-- you know, all the adults were scared so I was scared too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Number three, I didn't see anybody who I knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't see my sister, didn't see my uncle and aunt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just was with my cousin who was a year older and this scared me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said to myself, you know, I don't want to go anywhere on my own.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got to the train, which was-- it wasn't the regular train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was one of those cattle wagons with straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put 80 or whatever people on the-- on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I screamed very loudly, and my cousin screamed because I started to scream.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of people were wailing and crying, so it wasn't anything special, but maybe, could be that I screamed louder.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I know some German guard went to a Dutch policeman, asked what the-- what the commotion was all about.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
